bio:
Hello!
My name is Natallia and I'm a watercolor artist and illustrator.

I can provide illustrations for your project on a variety of topics - floral illustrations for wedding invitations, architecture, landscapes, animals and people, illustrations for children's books.

My skills:
-watercolor art;
-ink paintings;
-calligraphy (Sumi-e);
-pencil drawings;
-digital illustrations;
-basics of animation. 

